data.description: Forget long drives to the beach - live oceanside! Located on Galveston Island's Jamaica Beach, this cozy home offers the perfect amount of space for any gulf coast dweller. Enjoy the salty air on a large balcony-style porch or in the large yard shaded by tropical trees. Everything is close by, including a numerous array of restaurants, entertainment, and shopping. 20 minutes from I-45 leading into Houston. Call today!
